title: Scrapheap Challenge - 11x04 - Blow Football 1.avi
description:
"Dicks Diamonds" line-up includes regulars Dick Strawbridge, Jim Milner & guest Richard Little.

Their two challengers : "The Construction Cops" & "The Marcliffe Modifiers".

The challenge - to make a giant football blowing machine.

Please help me seed & get these 'out there' - I have a max. upload speed of c. 80k/s. The more help I get the quicker everyone gets them. 

I'm adding one episode a day Mon - Fri as they air on ABC2 digital TV here in Australia. (We're getting them before the UK)
